cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.HC

The paper focuses on the integration of visual content and external knowledge for food-related applications, which suggests a strong connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) for recipe analysis and retrieval. The exploration of food-related information in the context of restaurants also suggests a potential connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
